	"name":"Why is  Turtling 4 not allowed at Vorago?",
	"value": "Turtling 4, over Turtling 3, adds 1 tick to the duration of your barricade at the cost of 6 seconds of cooldown. In some particular instances that are quite easy to occur, this can lead to killing teammates if your cade is not off cooldown when you need it. Turtling 3 overcomes this, without substantially sacrificing your barricade duration.\nAnother option is bringing a second non-Turtling shield."
